Hiya,

Topic: UDP client and server application to reverse the given input sentence.
Compile: gcc file -o binary
Instructions to run:
  1. First, run the server binary (./server) to start the server.
  2. Then, run the client binary (./client) along with the the IP address
     and the port number. Something like: ./client 127.0.0.1 2102
  3. And you'll be able to see the results.
